## Input

```css
@debug value;
@warn value;
@error value;
@return value;
@use "theme";
@forward "theme";
@include button;
@content;
@extend .button;

@at-root .item {
	color: red;
}

@mixin button {
	color: red;
}

@if condition {
	color: red;
}

@else {
	color: red;
}

@for item from 1 through 3 {
	color: red;
}

@each item in list {
	color: red;
}

@while condition {
	color: red;
}

